      color - this is the color to set
      level - this is the level to set
      victoryPoints - these are the victory points to set
      cost - this is the cost of the card
      productionPowerInput - these are the resources to pay in input for a production to set
      productionPowerOutput - these are the resources gained in case of activation of the card to set
      productionPowerFaithPoints - these are the faith points gained in case of activation of the card to set
